How do I update this listing?




                                             International Value Advisers is based out of New York. International Value Advisers is a large advisory firm with  11-25 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $17,447,276,151 (Form ADV from 2017-04-03).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $3,143,200,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 63.75%. International Value Advisers's largest holding is Berkshire Hathaway Inc Class A with shares held of 1,951.  International Value Advisers has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 36 13Fs and  95 13D/G filings in our database for International Value Advisers. 
                                           






